{"in": {"title": "Questing Lores", "subtitle": "<span id=\"tr_lore_id\">the legend of fangs</span>", "lines": ["SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/fangs/0/jungle-morning.mp3 (no wait)", "TITLE: The Legend of Fangs the Fearless. Scene 1", "NARRATOR: The mouth of a cave in a dense forest. A fierce looking tiger is pacing near the entrance.", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/fangs/0/fangs-roar-001.mp3", "FANGS: That does it! Five days since a good night's sleep. I must do something about this.", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/fangs/0/fangs-shuffle-001.mp3", "FANGS: (fast) What was that?", "SMALL VOICE: (whisper) Worry not, dear Fangs. I will help you.", "FANGS: What? Who said that?", "SMALL VOICE: It was me. Peony.", "FANGS: Puny?", "SMALL VOICE: No. Peony. You have to pronounce the o.", "FANGS: Oh.", "SMALL VOICE: Yes. Like that.", "FANGS: Ah. There you are. What a tiny mouse! Maybe I should just eat you.", "PEONY: Perhaps. Do you think that will help you sleep?", "FANGS: Now that you mention it... No. In fact, I think I might even forget I ate you.", "PEONY: Well, then. What do you think?", "FANGS: Think what?", "PEONY: About listening to me.", "NARRATOR: Fangs rests his chin on his fist and thinks.", "FANGS: OK. I guess you're right. I have nothing to lose by listening to you.", "PEONY: And nothing to gain by eating me.", "FANGS: Yeah. That too.", "FANGS: But why do you want to help me? What's in it for you?", "PEONY: Why don't you ask me this question after you've had a good night's sleep, Fangs?", "FANGS: You bet I will Peony. And you better hope you have a good answer. If this is a trick, it'll be your last.", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/fangs/0/jungle-morning-r.mp3 (no wait)", "PEONY: Snoozlestones.", "FANGS: Hey! What did you just call me?", "PEONY: No. I meant Snoozlestones. You need to find them if you want to sleep.", "FANGS: Noodlebones?", "PEONY: No. Not Noodlebones. Those are dangerous. You need Snoozlestones.", "FANGS: And where do I find them... these Snoozlebones?", "PEONY: Snoozlestones. You can find them out there.", "FANGS: What do you mean out there?", "PEONY: Out there. In the real world. In the city.", "FANGS: Out there?", "PEONY: Yes. Out there.", "FANGS: But I'm not king of the jungle there. I don't even know my way around in the city.", "PEONY: No. Think of this as a chance. A chance to see what it's like when you're not king.", "FANGS: But I like being king.", "PEONY: Then that's all you'll know.", "FANGS: What do you mean?", "PEONY: I mean no Snoozlestones for us then.", "FANGS: (fast) No no. Wait. You know the city, don't you? Can you show me the way?", "PEONY: Yes. In fact, I even know who can help us find Snoozlestones in the city.", "FANGS: Terrific. Let's go. You can be my page. I still get to king over you in the land of unruly men.", "PEONY: And you can always rely on me to help you every way I can.", "FANGS: Well! What are we waiting for? Let's go then.", "PEONY: Not so fast, Tiger. You can't enter a city like this. They don't like stray cats.", "FANGS: I can see why you like it so much.", "PEONY: That's why nobody knows the city better than I do.", "FANGS: Good. You can tell me what to do then.", "SCENE: https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/fangs/0/jungle-morning-r.mp3 (no wait)", "PEONY: Well, you could learn to speak like humans for a start.", "FANGS: Like humans?", "PEONY: Yes. Like humans.", "FANGS: Is that even possible?", "PEONY: You'll be surprised. Start with something easy.", "FANGS: Like what?", "PEONY: I don't know... Maybe a greeting. How about \"Good morning\"?", "FANGS: Good moan-ing?", "PEONY: (pause) On second thought... Make it \"Hi there.\"", "FANGS: Hide there?", "PEONY: (pause) Ok. Now we know what we have to work with. How about just \"hello world\" then?", "FANGS: (x-slow) Hello World?", "PEONY: Yes, just like that.", "FANGS: Hello world?", "PEONY: Way to go, Fangs.", "PEONY: (x-loud) Fangs?!", "FANGS: I can't hear you", "PEONY: My review of your performance was spot on, in my professional opinion.", "NARRATOR: Peony swerves directly in front of Fangs.", "FANGS: (x-loud)(fast) Oh my gosh! and you call me reckless?", "PEONY: Yes i DO!", "FANGS: When I sleep Ill have you know my wellbeing and rest come first!", "PEONY: (x-loud)I'm going to finish my sentence! My review of your performance was spot on!", "PEONY: I see some real genius in your sleep habits, but I can't say that out here.", "PEONY: I was afraid all the animals would see right through me.", "PEONY: I don't want anyone to know that I've fallen for you.", "FANGS: Your'e saying this only to make me sick", "PEONY: (x-loud)No!", "PEONY: I'm saying it because it's true. Inside of us we both know you love to nap and slumber in your cave. Its part of who you are and if you dont find a way to fall asleep you'll regret it.", "FANGS: no, no I won't", "PEONY: Maybe not today, or tomorrow, but soon! and for the rest of your life you'll be tired.", "FANGS: But what about us?", "PEONY:We'll always have nap time, we didn't have we, we'd lose it, until you came to notice me under your paws. We got it back earlier today.", "FANGS: I said I was tired.", "PEONY: And you always will. But I've got job to do too.&nbsp;", "PEONY: Where I'm going you can't follow. What I've got to do you can't be any part of. FANGS, I'm no good at being noble, but it doesn't take much to see that the problems of restlessness don't amount to a hill of coconuts in this wild jungle world.", "FANGS: Someday your eyes will open and youll understand my life", "PEONY: Here's looking at you FANGS."], "speaker_map": {"NARRATOR": "Matthew", "SCENE": "Matthew", "TITLE": "Joanna", "SMALL VOICE": "Raveena", "FANGS": "Brian", "PEONY": "Raveena"}}, "out": {"cache_id": "2d4a63de8142228b18a2f8f99f95c904", "audio_objects": [["https://lores.nonlinearmedia.org/res/mp3/fangs/0/jungle-morning.mp3", 1], ["5db5aef5b4f3afaeb6fc327276727720-the-legend-of-fangs-the-f--